Description :
        Alpha Wooyeon promised eternity with his childhood friend and omega Eonhyeong, but one day Eonhyeong disappeared without saying goodbye.For several years, Woo-yeon searches for his first love, which he believes is his destiny.Several years later, he reunites with Eonhyeong at a social club he didn't want to attend, but after meeting Eonhyeong again, he surprisingly admits that he has always been an alpha. Wooyeon felt fed up with Eonhyeong, who also happened to be an alpha, and became confused... It couldn't be true that my fateful first love was an alpha.Similar magnetic poles will eventually collide with each Other+
